  "text": "It is three in the morning, the baby is crying, and you are googling the same question you asked yesterday. There has to be a better way. Meet Mira. The calm companion that actually knows your baby. Track feeds, sleep and diapers with a single tap. Your whole day, right there, at a glance. Free. But Mira is more than a tracker. She reads your logs. So when you ask a question, she already knows Mia napped once today and last eight two hours ago, real answers. For your baby, not a textbook. Go premium to unlock your full parenting advisor. Calm mode to guide you through the hard moments. And clean reports. Ready for your next pediatrician visit. Everything private. Everything on your phone. Mira. Parenting a little lighter.",
